<h1><a name="differences" id="differences">Differences</a></h1>
<div class="level1">

<p>

This shows you the differences between two versions of the page.
</p>

</div>
    <table class="diff">
    <tr>
    <th colspan="2" >
    <a class="wikilink1" href="/wiki:faculty_position_-_interview_questions?rev=1452327590">wiki:faculty_position_-_interview_questions [Sat Jan  9 08:19:50 2016]</a><br /><span class="user">jenny</span> <span class="sum">created</span>    </th>
    <th colspan="2" >
    <a class="wikilink1" href="/wiki:faculty_position_-_interview_questions">wiki:faculty_position_-_interview_questions [Sat Jan  9 08:47:28 2016]</a> (current)<br /><span class="user">jenny</span>     </th>
    </tr>
    <tr><td class="diff-blockheader" colspan="2">Line 1:</td>
<td class="diff-blockheader" colspan="2">Line 1:</td></tr>
<tr><td>-</td><td class="diff-deletedline"><strong>The following questions were asked during phone interviews for tenure-track faculty </strong>positions <strong>at private liberal arts colleges and Cal State Universities.</strong></td><td>+</td><td class="diff-addedline"><strong>====== Faculty </strong>positions <strong>- interview questions ======</strong></td></tr>
<tr><td> </td><td class="diff-context"></td><td> </td><td class="diff-context"></td></tr>
<tr><td>-</td><td class="diff-deletedline"><strong>====== General ====== </strong></td><td>+</td><td class="diff-addedline"><strong>The following questions </strong>were <strong>asked during phone interviews for tenure-track faculty positions </strong>at <strong>private liberal arts colleges </strong>and <strong>Cal State Universities. </strong>(<strong>Questions in bold were frequently asked.</strong>)</td></tr>
<tr><td>-</td><td class="diff-deletedline"><strong>* Why are you interested in the position at our school? </strong></td><td>+</td><td class="diff-addedline"></td></tr>
<tr><td>-</td><td class="diff-deletedline"><strong>* What strengths will you bring to our department and/or school? In other words, tell us why should we hire you? </strong></td><td>+</td><td class="diff-addedline"></td></tr>
<tr><td>-</td><td class="diff-deletedline"><strong>* If you </strong>were <strong>to put yourself in our shoes, looking </strong>at <strong>your CV, what do you think would make us pause, </strong>and <strong>why is this concern not an actual concern? </strong></td><td>+</td><td class="diff-addedline"></td></tr>
<tr><td>-</td><td class="diff-deletedline"><strong>* Why would you not want to come to this school? </strong>(<strong>reasons that might make you hesitate</strong>)</td><td>+</td><td class="diff-addedline"></td></tr>
<tr><td> </td><td class="diff-context"></td><td> </td><td class="diff-context"></td></tr>
<tr><td>-</td><td class="diff-deletedline">=====<strong>= Research =</strong>===== </td><td>+</td><td class="diff-addedline">===== <strong>General </strong>===== </td></tr>
<tr><td>-</td><td class="diff-deletedline">* <strong>Describe your research (in layman's terms). </strong></td><td>+</td><td class="diff-addedline">&nbsp;<strong> * </strong>**Why <strong>are you interested in the position at our school</strong>?<strong>**</strong> </td></tr>
<tr><td>-</td><td class="diff-deletedline">* Why <strong>is your research important</strong>? </td><td>+</td><td class="diff-addedline">&nbsp;<strong> </strong>* What <strong>strengths will you bring </strong>to <strong>our department and/or school</strong>? <strong>In other words, tell us why should we hire you</strong>? </td></tr>
<tr><td>-</td><td class="diff-deletedline">* What <strong>were your contributions </strong>to <strong>your research</strong>?<strong> </strong></td><td>+</td><td class="diff-addedline">&nbsp;<strong> </strong>* <strong>If </strong>you <strong>were to put yourself </strong>in our <strong>shoes, looking at your CV, what do you think would make us pause, and why is this concern not an actual concern</strong>? </td></tr>
<tr><td>-</td><td class="diff-deletedline"><strong>* What are your research plans for the next 2-3 (5) years</strong>? </td><td>+</td><td class="diff-addedline">&nbsp;<strong> </strong>* <strong>Why would </strong>you <strong>not want to come to this school? </strong>(<strong>reasons that might make you hesitate</strong>)<strong> </strong></td></tr>
<tr><td>-</td><td class="diff-deletedline">* <strong>How do </strong>you <strong>intend on conduct research, knowing that you may be the only person in your area </strong>in our <strong>department</strong>? </td><td>+</td><td class="diff-addedline"><strong> &nbsp;* **Do you have any questions for us</strong>?<strong>**</strong></td></tr>
<tr><td>-</td><td class="diff-deletedline">* <strong>How will </strong>you <strong>involve </strong>(<strong>non-PhD</strong>) <strong>students at the undergraduate (and Masters level, depending on the school) in your research</strong>?</td><td>+</td><td class="diff-addedline"></td></tr>
<tr><td> </td><td class="diff-context"></td><td> </td><td class="diff-context"></td></tr>
<tr><td>-</td><td class="diff-deletedline">=====<strong>= Teaching =</strong>===== </td><td>+</td><td class="diff-addedline">===== <strong>Research </strong>===== </td></tr>
<tr><td>-</td><td class="diff-deletedline">* <strong>Tell us of a time and a specific example when you had trouble explaining a concept and then later found a better way of explaining it. </strong></td><td>+</td><td class="diff-addedline">&nbsp;<strong> </strong>* *<strong>*Describe your research </strong>(<strong>in layman's terms</strong>)<strong>.*</strong>* </td></tr>
<tr><td>-</td><td class="diff-deletedline">* (<strong>Variant of the same thing</strong>) <strong>Tell us about your teaching philosophy: describe a moment when you were particularly effective at teaching and what was your approach/thinking? </strong></td><td>+</td><td class="diff-addedline">&nbsp;<strong> </strong>* <strong>Why is your research important</strong>? </td></tr>
<tr><td>-</td><td class="diff-deletedline">* <strong>What do you love most about teaching?</strong> </td><td>+</td><td class="diff-addedline">&nbsp;<strong> </strong>* What <strong>were your contributions </strong>to <strong>your research</strong>? </td></tr>
<tr><td>-</td><td class="diff-deletedline">* <strong>What courses do you want to teach</strong>? </td><td>+</td><td class="diff-addedline">&nbsp;<strong> * *</strong>*What are <strong>your research plans for the next 2-3 (5) years</strong>?<strong>**</strong> </td></tr>
<tr><td>-</td><td class="diff-deletedline">* What <strong>courses are you able </strong>to <strong>teach</strong>? </td><td>+</td><td class="diff-addedline">&nbsp;<strong> </strong>* <strong>How do </strong>you <strong>intend on conducting research, knowing that you may </strong>be <strong>the only person </strong>in your area <strong>in our department</strong>? </td></tr>
<tr><td>-</td><td class="diff-deletedline">* What <strong>courses </strong>are <strong>you not willing to teach</strong>? </td><td>+</td><td class="diff-addedline">&nbsp;<strong> </strong>* <strong>Given that the teaching load is 2 </strong>courses <strong>a semester, and we have no PhD students (to use as minions), how do </strong>you <strong>plan on remaining active </strong>in <strong>your research while offering our undergrads excellent instruction</strong>? </td></tr>
<tr><td>-</td><td class="diff-deletedline">* <strong>Will </strong>you be <strong>comfortable teaching a course not </strong>in your area <strong>of expertise</strong>? </td><td>+</td><td class="diff-addedline">&nbsp;<strong> </strong>* <strong>Given that the </strong>teaching <strong>load is 4 courses a semester, and we have no PhD </strong>students <strong>(to use as minions), how do you plan on remaining active in your research while offering our undergrads excellent instruction</strong>? </td></tr>
<tr><td>-</td><td class="diff-deletedline">* <strong>What </strong>courses <strong>would </strong>you <strong>be interested </strong>in <strong>developing</strong>? </td><td>+</td><td class="diff-addedline">&nbsp;<strong> </strong>* <strong>**How will </strong>you <strong>involve (non-PhD) students at </strong>the <strong>undergraduate (and Masters level, depending on the school) in your research</strong>?<strong>**</strong> </td></tr>
<tr><td>-</td><td class="diff-deletedline">* <strong>Cal States: How do you deal with </strong>teaching students <strong>of different levels of ability</strong>? </td><td>+</td><td class="diff-addedline">&nbsp;<strong> </strong>* <strong>What equipment do </strong>you <strong>need </strong>to <strong>do your research? (Cal State)</strong></td></tr>
<tr><td>-</td><td class="diff-deletedline">* <strong>What are </strong>you <strong>like in </strong>the <strong>classroom</strong>? </td><td>+</td><td class="diff-addedline"></td></tr>
<tr><td>-</td><td class="diff-deletedline">* <strong>Describe how </strong>you <strong>prepare </strong>to <strong>teach for a class you have never taught before.</strong></td><td>+</td><td class="diff-addedline"></td></tr>
<tr><td> </td><td class="diff-context"></td><td> </td><td class="diff-context"></td></tr>
<tr><td>-</td><td class="diff-deletedline">====== <strong>Other </strong>====== </td><td>+</td><td class="diff-addedline">===== <strong>Teaching </strong>==<strong>=== </strong></td></tr>
<tr><td>-</td><td class="diff-deletedline">* What would you do to help mentor students from under-represented minorities and women? </td><td>+</td><td class="diff-addedline"><strong> &nbsp;* Tell us of a time and a specific example when you had trouble explaining a concept and then later found a better way of explaining it. </strong></td></tr>
<tr><td>-</td><td class="diff-deletedline">* What is your ideal academic environment? </td><td>+</td><td class="diff-addedline"><strong> &nbsp;* (Variant of the same thing) Tell us about your teaching philosophy: describe a moment when you were particularly effective at teaching and what was your approach/thinking? </strong></td></tr>
<tr><td>-</td><td class="diff-deletedline">* How will you adjust from your current environment to <strong>teaching </strong>at our school? </td><td>+</td><td class="diff-addedline"><strong> &nbsp;* What do you love most about teaching? </strong></td></tr>
<tr><td>-</td><td class="diff-deletedline">* How will you contribute to our school's mission statement?</td><td>+</td><td class="diff-addedline"><strong> &nbsp;* **What courses do you want to teach?** </strong></td></tr>
<tr><td colspan="2">&nbsp;</td><td>+</td><td class="diff-addedline"><strong> &nbsp;* What courses are you able to teach? </strong></td></tr>
<tr><td colspan="2">&nbsp;</td><td>+</td><td class="diff-addedline"><strong> &nbsp;* What courses are you not willing to teach? </strong></td></tr>
<tr><td colspan="2">&nbsp;</td><td>+</td><td class="diff-addedline"><strong> &nbsp;* **Will you be comfortable teaching a course not in your area of expertise?** </strong></td></tr>
<tr><td colspan="2">&nbsp;</td><td>+</td><td class="diff-addedline"><strong> &nbsp;* What courses would you be interested in developing? </strong></td></tr>
<tr><td colspan="2">&nbsp;</td><td>+</td><td class="diff-addedline"><strong> &nbsp;* **How do you deal with teaching students of different levels of ability? (Cal State)** </strong></td></tr>
<tr><td colspan="2">&nbsp;</td><td>+</td><td class="diff-addedline"><strong> &nbsp;* What are you like in the classroom? </strong></td></tr>
<tr><td colspan="2">&nbsp;</td><td>+</td><td class="diff-addedline"><strong> &nbsp;* Describe how you prepare to teach for a class you have never taught before. </strong></td></tr>
<tr><td colspan="2">&nbsp;</td><td>+</td><td class="diff-addedline"><strong> </strong></td></tr>
<tr><td colspan="2">&nbsp;</td><td>+</td><td class="diff-addedline"><strong>===== Other (rarely asked) </strong>===== </td></tr>
<tr><td colspan="2">&nbsp;</td><td>+</td><td class="diff-addedline">&nbsp;<strong> </strong>* What would you do to help mentor students from under-represented minorities and women? </td></tr>
<tr><td colspan="2">&nbsp;</td><td>+</td><td class="diff-addedline">&nbsp;<strong> </strong>* What is your ideal academic environment? </td></tr>
<tr><td colspan="2">&nbsp;</td><td>+</td><td class="diff-addedline">&nbsp;<strong> </strong>* How will you adjust from your current environment to <strong>working </strong>at our school? </td></tr>
<tr><td colspan="2">&nbsp;</td><td>+</td><td class="diff-addedline">&nbsp;<strong> </strong>* How will you contribute to our school's mission statement? <strong>(Jesuit school)</strong></td></tr>
    </table>
    
